$$
\begin{aligned}
& =\left.\frac{y^{1 / 3+1}}{\frac{1}{3}+1}\right|_0 ^8=\left.\frac{3}{4}\left(y^{4 / 3}\right)\right|_0 ^8 \\
& =\frac{3}{4}\left[(8)^{4 / 3}-0\right]=\frac{3}{4}\left[2^4\right] \\
& =\frac{3}{4} \times 16=12 \text { sq. unit. }
\end{aligned}
$$
